Architecture
You can check the diagram above for the overall process. The CDK Deployment code constructs the following infrastructure:

Root Stack
Authentication Stack (Nested)
- Cognito User Pool
- Cognito Identity Pool
- Cognito Groups
- Cognito Client
- IAM Roles

Depends on

AppSync Stack (Nested)
- AppSync API
- RDS DataSource

Depends on

Lambdas Stack (Nested)
- Shared IAM Role
- Shared Code Asset
- Shared Layer
- VPC Configuration (imported)

Depends on

AppSync Resolvers Stack (Nested)
- AppSync Resolvers
- Lambda DataSources

Depends on

State Machines Stack (Nested)
- All Step Functions

Depends on

Frontend Stack (Nested)
- S3 Bucket
- CloudFront Distribution
- Route53 CNAME Entry

Depends on

Scheduled Inlet: (Prod Only)
- Data Import (Step Functions, Lambda)
- DB Dump
